description: First ever NFT project deployed on FEVM mainnet. Just minutes after FEVM went online, [FilPunks](https://www.filpunks.io/#) were deployed to celebrate Pi day with the community so that people could interact and have fun with FEVM right away. Riding the excitement of FEVM launch, Filpunks had garnered about 300 real FEVM users to mint and exchange NFTs on FEVM! Filpuks has been showcased in multiple explorers [here](https://filfox.info/en/token/f410f67hkuxnhgbnyonq7tw3kgaf5nv2mm5gsqrl67mq?t=tx), [here](https://filscan.io/en/nft/0xf7ceaa5da7305b87361f9db6a300bd6d74c674d2/) & [here](https://fvm.starboard.ventures/explorer/address/f410f67hkuxnhgbnyonq7tw3kgaf5nv2mm5gsqrl67mq) and contract is open sourced [here](https://fvm.starboard.ventures/explorer/address/f410f67hkuxnhgbnyonq7tw3kgaf5nv2mm5gsqrl67mq). Filpunks has minted about [1500 NFTs](https://filfox.info/en/token/f410f67hkuxnhgbnyonq7tw3kgaf5nv2mm5gsqrl67mq?t=tx) since then and look forward to have more to join FilPunks!
end_user: Dapp user, NFT collectors, Filecoin ecosystem participants, on-chain activities will be all benefiting from the project.
